ss but timing is key to get a good photo I was there just when the sun was glaring so I couldnt get a good photo but in the inside you can see the same photo so I took it inside loved this store would definitely visit again I hope the next time they have more jong-ho love you hello82 LA and thank you for what you do the girls working there were very helpful even though me and wife and her best friends kept interrupting them every time we saw something else ateez lol but they were understanding we also got 8 tokens for official hello82 photo cards", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Rich Cowboy", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108730243187965376727/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCy9bPr1QnW4hJ0RSB--ERhNo32AISDo4yzd0rPKcmDmqqqJU=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-05T22:33:40.595265002Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201Q2JXcFBUVFU0TVUxSU1ITlFTRVJNU25oQmRrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201Q2JXcFBUVFU0TVUxSU1ITlFTRVJNU25oQmRrRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b9e13c83bc1b:0xda2cb3335860e76c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJG7yDPOG5woARbOdgWDOzLNo/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURWczRfSDdRRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 years ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "They always hold the best pop ups for ateez. Thank you guys so much for the signed albums. I hope you guys can get more artists to work with you. Thank you for being LA based. The inside is so nicely decorated and colorful.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "They always hold the best pop ups for ateez. Thank you guys so much for the signed albums. I hope you guys can get more artists to work with you. Thank you for being LA based. The inside is so nicely decorated and colorful.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Lesly Cermeno", "